      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASCINATE KATH (5) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fourth (30.12) at this track. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Better than last start and worth following up. SAINT RICO (4) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 4/5 winner three back (24.81) at Goulburn over 440m. Well placed here and can atone this time. QUEEN OF SPADES (2) is a last start placegetter when a 3.5 lengths third at Wagga over 400m (23.35). Missed the frame only look here. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature. LONG ISLAND BLUE (1) looks an each-way chance.",
